sequenceDiagram
    actor Worker as Muncitor
    participant UI as Frontend React
    participant API as ActivityController
    participant Service as ActivityService
    participant DB as MySQL

    Worker->>UI: Completeaza raportul de finalizare
    UI->>API: Trimite cererea de finalizare
    API->>Service: updateActivityStatus(dto, utilizatorCurent)

    Service->>DB: Preia activitatea si resursele asociate
    DB-->>Service: Returneaza activitatea, stocurile si utilajele

    Service->>Service: Verifica muncitorul alocat
    Service->>Service: Valideaza intervalul, consumurile si recolta
    Service->>DB: Actualizeaza activitatea si consumurile reale
    Service->>DB: Scade stocurile si actualizeaza orele utilajelor

    alt activitate de recoltare
        Service->>DB: Actualizeaza istoricul culturii
    end

    Service->>DB: Salveaza notificari pentru manager si agronom
    DB-->>Service: Confirma actualizarea

    Service-->>API: Activitate finalizata
    API-->>UI: Raspuns de succes
    UI-->>Worker: Lucrarea apare ca finalizata
